ExpSyntax.val: 'Datum t/m mag niet kleiner zijn dan Datum vanaf !'

SQL_STMT_U.val: with wl as (select wlg_internetoptionco, count(*) as TotPerOption from :1 where wlg_date between ':3' and ':4' group by wlg_internetoptionco) select wl.wlg_internetoptionco, wo.wop_optiondescriptio, TotPerOption, (select sum(wl.TotPerOption) from wl) as total from wl, :2 wo where wo.wop_internetoptionco = wl.wlg_internetoptionco order by wl.wlg_internetoptionco
